These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Music-Genre: house, salsa, techno, d&b
1. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:house##1
2. Food:mango == Music-Genre:d&b##1
3. Music-Genre:techno is on the right of Music-Genre:house##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Music-Genre:d&b##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Music-Genre:house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | house     | techno   | d&b |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Birthday: november, september, december, march
Sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. Birthday:march == Sport:soccer##1
2. Birthday:november is on the far right##1
3. Birthday:september is on the right of Birthday:march##1
4. Birthday:march is on the right of Sport:swimming##1
5. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | march | september | november    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Hobby: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
Transport: train, bus, helicopter, tram
1. Transport:helicopter is on the left of Transport:tram##1
2. Hobby:fishing == Transport:train##1
3. Transport:bus is on the far right##1
4. Transport:tram is on the right of Hobby:writing##1
5. Hobby:traveling is on the left of Transport:bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Transport   | train   | helicopter | tram | bus         |

