.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
Transport: train, tram, snowmobile, ship
Music-Genre: blues, d&b, disco, r&b
1. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Music-Genre:blues##1
2. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of Music-Genre:disco##1
3. Transport:ship is on the right of Transport:train##1
4. Transport:snowmobile is on the far left##1
5. Transport:tram == Music-Genre:disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Transport      | snowmobile | tram  | train | ship |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | disco | r&b           | d&b   |

